{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I didn't want to join, whether it's Fascism, Communism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This to me, I don't want to join.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I kept postponing and postponing, and I'll think and I'll do this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, I am not so sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The pressure became eventually terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after my brother-- while my brother was still dead, somehow, we managed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after my brother left, I said to myself, now, I don't want this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just want to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually-- again, my uncle, the one who was waiting for refugees at the Joint in Budapest, he arranged that I join a group who would smuggle through many, many borders, Romania, Hungary, Hungary, Austria, Austria, US-occupied Germany, to Munich, where one of his daughters was.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was the one who told me about my brother Alex, because when he left, he too went the same route and stayed with her and her husband.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, they just got married, because that was her childhood sweetheart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was the one who told me that my brother joined the Haganah and to Marseilles and from there, he was fighting the War of Independence.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
